snippet.title: Noble's Life: Kingdom Reborn Trailer
snippet.description:
War has spilled over your lands!

Become a medieval noble in a unique combination of realistic simulator and strategy. Grow your realm through a wide variety of decisions, command real-time defenses in epic sieges, and organize raids into enemy lands. Find your ruling style!

Add to Steam Wishlist now:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1662050/Nobles_Life_Kingdom_Reborn/

Like us on Facebook:
